    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving power plant delivers linear power up to an 8,400 RPM redline through a precise 6-speed manual transmission. The vehicle features the M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for optimized lateral dynamics. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement with treated shells and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the longevity of the high-tension internals. The rear subframe and bushings remain tight, and the hydraulic steering rack provides exceptional communicative feedback. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its driver-focused history, the structural integrity and drivetrain synchronization are excellent. A purist\u2019s spec ready for immediate spirited use.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
