      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly balances performance and everyday utility. The exterior features a vibrant, glossy paint finish that has been regularly waxed; upon close inspection, you may find only minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel, typical of responsible ownership. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather seats are plush and supportive, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's bolster. All interior technology, including the infotainment screen, backup camera, and heated seats, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises. It comes with a complete maintenance log, including a recent oil service and a fresh cabin air filter. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced last season. This car drives straight and true, offering a quiet and comfortable ride for its next owner.",
